{"tid":1556681,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"HKCC之友有嘢講","createTime":"2019-09-09T23:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T16:52:19.000Z","uid":320329,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81b58bcbc47f6575060206d42ce9ae8159b99dd5","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:45:59.000Z","msg":"噚日和理鏈活動非常成功，不單止可以團結我哋理工及CC學生「鏈成一線」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更加喚起左各界嘅關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位理工人俾啲掌聲自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說尋日小弟好夜放學，已經好攰，所以冇加入人鏈活動。但係望著理工人鏈一直延綿到本部嗰下，內心其實非常之澎湃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想跟埋嗌一份！但係因為跟住friend放學，又唔敢嗌，最後只係敢望住各位行過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能我生得衰，有D巴絲回避我眼神，不過我想講：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋都喺鏈成一線架</span></span>噚日返到屋企之後諗咗好耐：如果我有一齊企既、一齊嗌，多一份力量，我哋嘅影響力會唔會更大？自己個心真係好唔舒服。我應承你哋，下次一撚定一齊嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家亦唔好因為有人白白行過就灰心，其實我哋好多人都只係好攰所以無幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在此呼籲所有理工及CC之友，下次咩活動都好，一齊上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大算求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n理工人CC人好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8d49fc882842b38eae6095002eb7697c1a7a86","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:46:23.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"216d21e4b6337bd64f88bbfe8d5a2b847b6c2a9e","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:46:35.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"414887f225dd2c09b460db6c44f831d05582875a","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:46:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"9414297a676767b9cc9bd52a40214559376bfa6b","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:47:13.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"fa5d8ea5bae03b37e8d65202fad0ea1d0860268f","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:47:30.000Z","msg":"沒有暴徒"},{"pid":"f218b0e5a578262e1b7e6f4b670a789738a6167c","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:47:45.000Z","msg":"只有暴證"},{"pid":"1b3591103ba5231ec8282fdce941f1338f89f022","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:47:57.000Z","msg":"香港人"},{"pid":"0a15b87625a6e51bbfeab854a9d5f4e61b1849c3","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:48:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"f5cce6ce3af1e51b0109d138add39353b192c401","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港人治港"},{"pid":"ce4e7696d11c37c211829cca2c26e05abe53fc10","tid":1556681,"uid":308486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"如果hhb wk PolyU組得成人鏈都幾震撼<br />\n但要好多人"},{"pid":"febfb73547b284f89d2a527ac11275901bd4b623","tid":1556681,"uid":320329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce4e7696d11c37c211829cca2c26e05abe53fc10","tid":1556681,"uid":308486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"如果hhb wk PolyU組得成人鏈都幾震撼<br />\n但要好多人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=